These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-1::.
4 different pets are kept: bird, ferret, horse, fish
1. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
2. the owner of the ferret is somewhere between the owner of the horse and the owner of the fish##7
3. the owner of the horse is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |  2   |   3   |  4   |
| Pet   | horse | ferret | fish | bird |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-2::.
There 4 different types of food: kiwi, garlic, pineapple, cabbage
1. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person eating cabbage##1
2. the person eating pineapple is somewhere between the person eating garlic and the person eating kiwi##7
3. the person eating pineapple is between the person eating garlic and the person eating cabbage##2

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Food   | kiwi | cabbage | pineapple | garlic |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-3::.
