.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-4::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, taxi, car, skateboard
1. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere between the person driving the car and the person driving the taxi##7
2. the person driving the bus is somewhere to the left of the person driving the skateboard##5
3. the person driving the bus is between the person driving the skateboard and the person driving the car##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |   3   |    4    |
| Transport   | car | bus | skateboard | taxi |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-5::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, horror, action, scientific
1. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
2. the person watching horror movies is between the person watching epic movies and the person watching scientific movies##2
3. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the person watching action movies##3
4. the person watching epic movies is somewhere between the person watching action movies and the person watching scientific movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |   3   |      4       |
| Movie-Genre   | action | epic | horror | scientific |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-6::.
There are 4 different nationalities: italian, brazilian, dutch, polish
1. the italian is somewhere between the polish and the brazilian##7
2. the dutch is somewhere between the italian and the polish##7
3. the dutch is on the left or right of the polish##3
4. the dutch is somewhere to the right of the polish##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2   |     3     |    4    |
| Nationality   | polish | dutch | italian | brazilian |

