2. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere between the person drinking milk and the person drinking hot-chocolate##7
3. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the right of the person drinking coffee##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |    2     |   3   |      4      |
| Beverage   | coffee | milk | lemonade | hot-chocolate |

